 Bimbo Ademoye, a Nollywood actress, has revealed how she celebrated her 31st birthday and extended gratitude to everyone who took the time to wish her a happy birthday on social media and elsewhere. Bimbo Ademoye, a budding actress, expressed her gratitude for the outpouring of love, saying she felt on top of the world. READ MORE: Bimbo Ademoye Shares Stunning Pictures As She Turns 31 Bimbo Ademoye claims she spent the entire day filming in the jungle, but she enjoyed every minute of it. She wrote: THANK YOU! For all the birthday wishes. Thank you so much guys . I’m still responding to messages , returning calls. Whew, I couldn’t repost all the stories. But I see you all and I’m so grateful for the outpour of love , I felt on top of the world. See post below:   A post shared by Bimbo Ademoye (@bimboademoye) 